General Info

Scientific family: Asteraceae (same as sunflowers, chrysanthemums)

Genus: Bellis (common daisy: Bellis perennis)

Common names: Daisy, English daisy, Lawn daisy

Origin: Native to Europe and temperate regions of Asia

Life cycle: Perennial (some are annuals in warmer climates)

